{
  "name": "RPlog_35_ISY_Competition_Vapor_vs_Banger",
  "title": "Vapor vs. Banger",
  "summary": "In the 35 ISY fighter-simulator championship, Admiral Jal'Dana, flying as Vapor, draws Marshal Krieg Inrokana (Banger) as her first opponent and sets out to shake the rust from her command-dulled piloting skills. The seasoned Admiral relies on experience and cunning, hiding behind a small moon and striking hard and fast, while the younger Krieg falls into his combat zone and answers with snap rolls and close passes. The two trade blistering exchanges across many rounds, each respecting the other's edge. Their duel becomes a benchmark Krieg measures his later matches against, proof that Vapor still has the skill that earned her command. The hard-fought contest cements the mutual regard between Admiral and Marshal.",
